short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Shows a Bluesky user's activity graph embedded in their profile page

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension embeds a GitHub-style "activity graph" of a user's post activity into their Bluesky profile page.

This extension is open source software & you are encouraged to submit fixes and changes directly: https://github.com/rpj/bsky-post-freq-extn
